arStrings.szText: Thank you for one Hell of a year! You’ve reaped with untold ferocity and no gifts currently remain.  {c_highlight}From June 6th-June 12th, return here daily at 12:00 p.m. PDT for a new gift.{/c}  Claim them as yours until the 20th, when they are promptly destroyed by Hell’s minions.
